description:
In this coding challenge, I attempt to program a clock in the HTML5 canvas with the p5.js library. This challenge was inspired by John Maeda's "12 o'clocks" and Golan Levin's assignment on the subject in his 60212 Interactivity & Computation class.

💻Challenge: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/074-clock.html
